Mauricio Pochettino returns to former side Southampton for the first time since leaving last summer . 
 The Tottenham boss done an excellent job during his 16 month spell . 
 The Argentine manager has adopted the same methods at Spurs as he did during his time at St Mary's . 
 Pochettino blooded the likes of Calum Chambers and James Ward-Prowse while at Southampton, and has done the same with Harry Kane at Spurs . 
 His passing and pressing philosophy has taken a while for his new set of players to adjust to, though . 
 